<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Зоология: Хордовые — Тренажёр</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Unbounded:wght@400;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0d0f14;
    --surface: #161a24;
    --surface2: #1e2433;
    --border: #2a3045;
    --accent: #6ee7b7;
    --accent2: #818cf8;
    --warn: #f59e0b;
    --danger: #f87171;
    --text: #e8eaf0;
    --muted: #6b7280;
    --correct: #10b981;
    --wrong: #ef4444;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .progress-bar-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 300px;
    margin: 0 24px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .progress-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
  }
  .score-badge {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(110,231,183,0.1);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(110,231,183,0.2);
  }

  /* MAIN NAV */
  .main-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 20px 24px 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .main-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .nav-btn {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .nav-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent2); color: var(--text); }
  .nav-btn.active {
    background: rgba(129,140,248,0.15);
    border-color: var(--accent2);
    color: var(--accent2);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* SCREENS */
  .screen { display: none; padding: 24px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .screen.active { display: block; }

  /* HOME */
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 0 32px;
  }
  .hero-emoji { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 16px; display: block; }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero p { color: var(--muted); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 32px; }

  .mode-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .mode-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.25s;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .mode-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(110,231,183,0.1);
  }
  .mode-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
  .mode-card h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .mode-card p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* THEORY CARDS */
  .theory-group { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .theory-group-title {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .theory-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .theory-card-head {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .theory-card-head:hover { background: var(--surface2); }
  .theory-card-head h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
  .theory-card-head span { color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px; transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .theory-card-head.open span { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .theory-card-body {
    display: none;
    padding: 0 20px 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .theory-card-body.open { display: block; }
  .theory-card-body p { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: #c5c9d6; line-height: 1.7; }
  .theory-card-body ul { margin-top: 8px; padding-left: 18px; }
  .theory-card-body li { font-size: 13px; color: #c5c9d6; margin-bottom: 4px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(110,231,183,0.12);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-right: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(110,231,183,0.2);
  }
  .tag.purple {
    background: rgba(129,140,248,0.12);
    color: var(--accent2);
    border-color: rgba(129,140,248,0.2);
  }

  /* COMPARISON TABLE */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; margin-top: 8px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; min-width: 700px; }
  th {
    background: var(--surface2);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent2);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  td {
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: #c5c9d6;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  tr:hover td { background: var(--surface2); }
  .cell-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .cell-green { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.15); color: #10b981; }
  .cell-purple { background: rgba(129,140,248,0.15); color: #818cf8; }
  .cell-yellow { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); color: #f59e0b; }
  .cell-red { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.15); color: #f87171; }

  /* QUIZ */
  .quiz-container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .quiz-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .quiz-meta .q-num {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent2);
  }
  .question-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .question-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .question-hint {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .options { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .option {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: all 0.18s;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .option:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(129,140,248,0.08); }
  .option.correct { border-color: var(--correct); background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12); color: #6ee7b7; }
  .option.wrong { border-color: var(--wrong); background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); color: #fca5a5; }
  .option:disabled { cursor: default; }

  .feedback {
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    display: none;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .feedback.correct { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3); color: #6ee7b7; }
  .feedback.wrong { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.25); color: #fca5a5; }
  .feedback.show { display: block; }

  .btn {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #34d399);
    color: #0d1117;
    border: none;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 16px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .btn.secondary {
    background: var(--surface2);
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* RESULTS */
  .result-box {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 24px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
  }
  .result-emoji { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .result-box h2 {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .result-score {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    margin: 16px 0 8px;
  }

  /* FLASHCARDS */
  .flashcard-wrap { perspective: 1000px; max-width: 560px; margin: 24px auto; }
  .flashcard {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/2;
    position: relative;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transition: transform 0.55s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .flashcard.flipped { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
  .card-face {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .card-front { background: var(--surface); }
  .card-back {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f35, #161c2e);
    transform: rotateY(180deg);
    border-color: var(--accent2);
  }
  .card-face .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .card-front .label { color: var(--accent); }
  .card-back .label { color: var(--accent2); }
  .card-face h2 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.4; }
  .card-back h2 { font-size: 16px; color: #e0e4f0; }
  .card-hint { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 16px; }

  .fc-controls {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .fc-counter { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .btn-sm {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-sm:hover { border-color: var(--accent2); }
  .btn-sm.green { border-color: var(--correct); color: var(--correct); }
  .btn-sm.red { border-color: var(--wrong); color: var(--wrong); }

  /* MNEMONICS */
  .mnemonic-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .mnemonic-card h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .mnemonic-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #c5c9d6; line-height: 1.7; }
  .mnemonic-card .trick {
    margin-top: 10px;
    background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--warn);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* TIMELINE */
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 12px;
    top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  .tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -26px;
    top: 4px;
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent);
  }
  .tl-item h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .tl-item p { font-size: 13px; color: #a0a8be; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* SECTION TITLE */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Unbounded', sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: -16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 20px; }
    .mode-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .card-face h2 { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <div class="logo">🧬 Хордовые</div>
  <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
    <div class="progress-bar-fill" id="progressBar" style="width:0%"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="score-badge" id="scoreDisplay">0 ✦</div>
</div>

<nav class="main-nav">
  <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showScreen('home')">🏠 Главная</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showScreen('theory')">📖 Теория</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showScreen('table')">📊 Таблица</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="startFlashcards()">🃏 Карточки</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="startQuiz()">⚡ Тест</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showScreen('mnemonics')">🧠 Мнемоники</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showScreen('evolution')">🕐 Эволюция</button>
</nav>

<!-- HOME -->
<div id="screen-home" class="screen active">
  <div class="hero">
    <span class="hero-emoji">🦈</span>
    <h1>Выучи Хордовых<br>за 2 часа</h1>
    <p>7 классов животных, все системы органов, сравнительные признаки. Начни с теории, потом карточки, потом тест.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="mode-grid">
    <div class="mode-card" onclick="showScreen('theory')">
      <span class="mode-icon">📖</span>
      <h3>Теория</h3>
      <p>Весь материал по темам с раскрывающимися блоками</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-card" onclick="showScreen('table')">
      <span class="mode-icon">📊</span>
      <h3>Сравнение</h3>
      <p>Итоговая таблица по всем классам и системам</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-card" onclick="startFlashcards()">
      <span class="mode-icon">🃏</span>
      <h3>Карточки</h3>
      <p>Термин → определение. Перелистывай и запоминай</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-card" onclick="startQuiz()">
      <span class="mode-icon">⚡</span>
      <h3>Тест</h3>
      <p>40 вопросов с объяснениями правильных ответов</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-card" onclick="showScreen('mnemonics')">
      <span class="mode-icon">🧠</span>
      <h3>Мнемоники</h3>
      <p>Приёмы для запоминания сложных признаков</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-card" onclick="showScreen('evolution')">
      <span class="mode-icon">🕐</span>
      <h3>Эволюция</h3>
      <p>Хронология ароморфозов от ланцетника до человека</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:32px; background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:20px 24px;">
    <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--warn);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px;">⏱ Рекомендуемый план на 2 часа</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:8px 16px;font-size:14px;">
      <span style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">0–30 мин</span><span style="color:#c5c9d6;">Теория — читай раскрывая блоки по каждому классу</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">30–50 мин</span><span style="color:#c5c9d6;">Сравнительная таблица — смотри, запоминай паттерны</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">50–80 мин</span><span style="color:#c5c9d6;">Карточки — гони пока не ошибёшься менее 3 раз</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">80–110 мин</span><span style="color:#c5c9d6;">Тест — 40 вопросов, читай объяснения к ошибкам</span>
      <span style="color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;">110–120 мин</span><span style="color:#c5c9d6;">Мнемоники + повтор слабых мест</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- THEORY -->
<div id="screen-theory" class="screen">
  <div class="section-title">📖 Теория</div>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Нажми на заголовок чтобы раскрыть блок</p>

  <div id="theory-content"></div>
</div>

<!-- TABLE -->
<div id="screen-table" class="screen">
  <div class="section-title">📊 Сравнительная таблица</div>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Главные признаки всех классов хордовых</p>

  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Признак</th>
          <th>Ланцетник</th>
          <th>Круглоротые</th>
          <th>Хрящ. рыбы</th>
          <th>Костные рыбы</th>
          <th>Амфибии</th>
          <th>Рептилии</th>
          <th>Птицы</th>
          <th>Млекопит.</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><b>Сердце</b></td>
          <td>нет (брюшная аорта)</td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">2-камерное</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">2-камерное</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">2-камерное</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-yellow">3-камерное</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-yellow">3-камерное*</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-green">4-камерное</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-green">4-камерное</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><b>Кругов кровообращения</b></td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>2</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><b>Температура тела</b></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">холодная</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">холодная</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">холодная</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">холодная</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">холодная</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-red">холодная</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-green">тёплая 40-42°</span></td>
          <td><span class="cell-tag cell-green">тёплая 36-38°</span></td>
